title: Is Sean Quinn America’s next breakout rider? ‘I got my teeth kicked in a few times’
content:
The 23-year-old Californian completed his first grand tour: 'The Vuelta gave me a lot of perspective of where I am in my career.'

Read the full article at Is Sean Quinn America’s next breakout rider? ‘I got my teeth kicked in a few times’ on Velo.
